INSERT INTO scalar_tap_receipts_invalid (
                signer_address,
                signature,
                allocation_id,
                timestamp_ns,
                nonce,
                value
            ) SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::CHAR(40)[],
                $2::BYTEA[],
                $3::CHAR(40)[],
                $4::NUMERIC(20)[],
                $5::NUMERIC(20)[],
                $6::NUMERIC(40)[]
            )
